The Katsina State government has debunked the alleged report in one of the national daily that, the All Progressive Congress (APC), has zone it’s Governorship ticket to Katsina central. Al-Amin Isa, the Director General New Media to Governor Aminu Bello Masari stated this in a press statement made available to newsmen in Katsina at the weekend. “At no time in any of the numerous stakeholders meetings of Katsina APC has zoning been broached much less, a decision taken on the matter”. “The statement is only a figment of The Nation correspondent’s imagination”, it added. It therefore, urged the general public to disregard the said statement in its totality as its false, misleading and deliberately scripted to create chaos where there’s none.